Arsenal were locked in talks with Borussia Dortmund trying to agree a fee for central defender Sokratis Papastathopoulos.

The German club want £20million for the Greece international, who can also play right-back and holding midfielder.

Sportsmail first reported Arsenal's interest in the player today.

