The Gunners do not want to meet Dortmund's asking price and are trying to secure a reduced figure before pressing ahead with a swoop.

But manager Arsene Wenger knows he needs defensive cover before Monday's transfer deadline and is keen to land Papastathopoulos, who is understood to be open to joining Arsenal.

 

